unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Printed Ephemera Collection on the International Typographical Union
abstract_ssm: The Printed Ephemera Collection on the International Typographical Union is an artificial collection, collected and assembled by the staff of the Tamiment Library over the course of several decades.  The files contain agreements, contracts and constitutions, as well as printed ephemera such as fliers, leaflets, newspaper clippings, pamphlets and other publications.
